ble-gambling/images/footer_icon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkjc.com%2Fresponsible-gambling%2Fimages%2Ffooter_icon.jpg&h=f8bd194a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n靚相:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1iWgzJB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1iWgzJB.jpg&h=1a62a8cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n燈神介紹:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyH8vkn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyH8vkn.png&h=92614d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PyaqxyJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyaqxyJ.png&h=bfd1c2a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n神父靚圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/770riqm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F770riqm.png&h=af9129b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">新手須知</span><br />\n連登apps台既fgo post係主要討論<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\">日</span></span>ser<br />\n台服問題可免則免<br />\n以下內容只適用於<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\">日</span></span>ser<br />\n呢隻game三十石=十一抽<br />\n課金就650hkd左右=168石<br />\n假如你想長玩 最符合效率就係<br />\n你可以先係淘寶買個首抽ac(顧名思義係全新ac但係有石)<br />\n大概四十蚊到 入面有幾十符+900幾石<br />\n你冇睇錯只係四十蚊港紙左右<br />\n<br />\n刷到有3-4個五星 就可以選擇開局<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"gold\"><strong>-催post專用環保post-</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1422551/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1422551/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHfGH22.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHfGH22.gif&h=a73d85ce&s={SIZE}\" /></p>"},{"pid":"fff10bef5d7f6f7b3cfed98a141b95d5961bd145","tid":2120050,"uid":21723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T12:17:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://